snippet.title: Fight Night Round 4 PS3 Career Mode Gameplay Walkthrough Ep.2 - Professional Debut & 25 hf4hs
snippet.description:
Fight Night Round 4 PS3 Career Mode Gameplay Walkthrough Ep.2 - Professional Debut

Jesus Perez is ready fight. He's going to have to fight his way up the ranks in order to show the world that he's the best boxer around. He's from Puerto Rico, home to some of the best boxers in history.  He's going to train hard, think straight and box right. Can he become the best boxer ever?


Stay tuned!!!

Subscribe for more Fight Night Round 4: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCB1UOVNVFPMdkM9kYDjiqpg

Thanks for watching this Fight Night Round 4 video. If you enjoy this video, please like the video and subscribe if you haven't already.
